trans-unit.source: Contains the security settings associated with a peer channel, including the type of authentication used and the security used for the message transport.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder sikkerhetsinnstillinger som er knyttet til en node-kanalen, inkludert godkjenning brukes og sikkerheten som brukes for transport for meldingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new default instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerSecuritySettings"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny standardforekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerSecuritySettings"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the value that indicates the security mode of the peer channel.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir verdi som angir sikkerhetsmodus for node-kanal.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode> enumeration value that indicates the security mode for the peer channel.
The specified value is not an enumerated value from <xref:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode>
trans-unit.target: Den angitte verdien er ikke en tallverdi fra<xref:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode></xref:System.ServiceModel.SecurityMode>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the security mode information should be serialized.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om modus sikkerhetsinformasjonen skal serialiseres.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Boolean> that specifies <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the security mode information should be serialized, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if it should not be serialized..
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.Boolean>som angir <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> Hvis modus sikkerhetsinformasjonen skal serialiseres, og <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis det ikke skal serialiseres..</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the transport information should be serialized.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om transport informasjonen skal serialiseres.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Boolean> that specifies <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the transport information should be serialized, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if it should not be serialized..
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.Boolean>som angir <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> Hvis transport informasjonen skal serialiseres, og <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis det ikke skal serialiseres..</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: Gets the value that indicates the security settings for the transport used for messages transmitted over the peer channel.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir sikkerhetsinnstillingene for transport brukes for meldinger som overf√∏res via node-kanal.
